org.agorava.api.storage

Interface UserSessionRepository

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Identifiable, Iterable<OAuthSession>, Repository<OAuthSession>, Serializable

    public interface UserSessionRepository
extends Repository<OAuthSession>, Identifiable
    Allows to manage multiple OAuth Session. The connection to service are backed by a Set to avoid null or duplicate connection. Uniqueness of a connection is based on service type and User name on the service
